<lyrics>[V1]
 1- dwrt fy kl mkạn ʿn qlb zy qlbh
 ʿạrf kl ạlạ̉ḥzạn ḥs bqlby wmtạʿbh
 mạlqyt zy ḥbyby yswʿ ṣdyq ạ̉ḥkyh mạly
 dh ṭwl ạllyl lḥd ṭlwʿ ạlsẖms bạsẖky lh ḥạly
 2- dwrt mạ lqyt dwrt fy kl mkạn mạ lqyt
 dwrt fy kl ṭryq ʿn nbʿ ạlqlb dbl
 mḥkwm ʿlyh wbryʾ ṭb sẖkwth hạttqbl
 mạ lqyt zy ạ̹lhy qạḍy rqyq qlbh ḥnyn
 qạl jạny kẖrwfy dh sẖyʾ msẖ ʿạdy wdmʿh dh sẖyʾ msẖ hyn
 dwrt mạ lqyt dwrt wlqyt qlbk wlqạny</lyrics>
